&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="lessons-learned"&gt;Lessons Learned
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Terraform Initialization Order&lt;/b&gt;: Since the backend block is evaluated with the highest priority, dynamic injection of variables requires the use of -backend-config or maintaining static definitions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;S3 Key Strictness&lt;/b&gt;: The backend key requires the full path of the object rather than a prefix, so a trailing / is not allowed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;CI/CD Trigger Precision&lt;/b&gt;: In GitHub Actions paths filtering, recursive specification using ** is mandatory to capture all changes under a directory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>